title: PetRescue’s Best Friends’ Walk: Help Homeless Pets Find Homes
description: Walk your dog and support homeless pets. Join PetRescue's Best Friends' Walk to help find loving homes for pets in need this September.

title: Golden Retriever Meet Up at Bark Park
description: Enjoy fun, games, and new fur-riends at this exclusive event for Goldies. Join the Golden Retriever Meetup at Bark Park on September 7th!

title: Kyneton Dog Dash 2024
description: Enjoy a fun day out with your pup at the 40m Kyneton Dog Dash. Join fellow dog lovers in Kyneton for a tail-wagging good time this September!
